{"tid":1308328,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"八達通：2019年內 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 可透過 Apple Pay 使用八達通","createTime":"2019-07-12T00:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:00:25.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd665acbce2b04ae49e6a4c0f19d0599b330268","tid":1308328,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"八達通 iphone 版 apple pay 很多用家都在等 ，早前有傳聞表示在最新的 iOS 13 代碼中，顯示有八達通的代碼在 beta 版本中，因此推測八達通公司正在與蘋果公司合作，測試在 iPhone 上使用八達通，而現在終於正式確定，八達通公司表示，將會在 2019 年內，可在 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 上透過 Apple Pay ，使用八達通支付服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八達通公司表示：八達通卡有限公司一向致力提供創新的支付服務，以配合客戶多元化支付需要，公司宣布今年稍後，客戶將可在 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 上透過 Apple Pay ，使用八達通支付公共交通及零售交易。公司會於稍後公布更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n其實八達通公司早已在 Android 平台上，與 Samsung 合作，推出 Samsung Pay 支援八達通，可以將目前用戶手中的實體卡，轉到手機版本，目前尚未知道，可否將Samsung Pay 內的八達通，轉到 iPhone 手機上，一切估計要等到 iOS 13 正式推出後才知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/07/11/apple-pay-octopus/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2Fapple-pay-octopus%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0KCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=27496682\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/07/11/apple-pay-octopus/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"2a5913c8d8cf290590736f6b2bb96888e684056a","tid":1308328,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:08:35.000Z","msg":"遲晒到"},{"pid":"de553bd3d5fa1213de54c303f7f059e8c38ba8a4","tid":1308328,"uid":68896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:15:18.000Z","msg":"買apple watch 多個籍口了"},{"pid":"697f1df7bee5ec77548daa9aff691c9f659463f1","tid":1308328,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"隻apple watch 終於有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27de6f2f5d8ff4a23a419529579895232ab034b6","tid":1308328,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":